Now, all grown-up, high school juniors Kenny, Kelsey, Natalie, Brandon, Alexis, Nathan and Joel are gearing up to leave the family home in Des Moines, Iowa, and go solo.

Several of the teenagers have revealed that they're dating, with Brandon recently celebrating the ten-month mark with his girlfriend and Kelsey happy with a boyfriend of one year.

